a.xlink:title: This function tests the EigenStepper with the DefaultExtension and the DenseEnvironmentExtension. The focus of this tests lies in the choosing of the right extension for the individual use case. This is performed with three different detectors: a) Pure vacuum -> DefaultExtension needs to act b) Pure Be -> DenseEnvironmentExtension needs to act c) Vacuum - Be - Vacuum -> Both should act and switch during the propagation.
